title: Cloak golden gate — foyer, descriptions, blocked north exit
story: cloak-of-darkness
description: Room descriptions and traversal per the canonical cloak.story
  (design.md §3.1). Divergence 1 from Firth's original — the Outside room is
  replaced by a blocked north exit with the cant-leave phrase. Authored fresh
  as the ADR-210 AC-1 golden gate (frozen 2026-07-10); runs against the
  Chord-interpreted cloak.story, not the hand-written TS story.

# The bar is deliberately not entered in this file — entering it while
# carrying the cloak advances the message state (see message-*.transcript).
